This is a container to get versions.

Following commands are recognized:

f	Get fboot binary version
s	Get sboot binary version
m	Get supervisor binary version
a	Get tboot OTP version counter
b	Get supervisor OTP version counter

First load the container
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_version.img

Get fboot binary version
$ printf 'f' > f
$ cmtest data -f100 f
write data...0x064:1...read data...0x064:19...
00000000: 32 30 32 31 2d 31 31 2d  31 30 2d 67 31 62 62 38  |2021-11-10-g1bb8|
00000010: 65 30 37                                          |e07|
OK

15:37:56,654 +0.0063: [CLO] main:86: Sample (version) container starting...
15:37:56,934 +0.2798: [CLO] main:110: Received sic message from 0x801
15:37:56,937 +0.0033: [CLO] process_data:57: Fboot version: 2021-11-10-g1bb8e07

Get sboot binary version
$ printf 's' > s
$ cmtest data -f100 s

Get supervisor binary version
$ printf 'm' > m
$ cmtest data -f100 m
